high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the bathroom, then turn to your right at the brick wall on your left, and go to the counter space between the two sinks.
Pick up the soap dispenser closest to the edge of the counter top.
Turn to your left and go across the bathroom and turn right just before the toilet, where the garbage can is on the floor, between the toilet and the sink.
Place the soap dispenser in the garbage can.
Go to the toilet in front of you.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the back of the toilet.
Turn to the garbage can on the floor.
Place the soap dispenser in the garbage can, in front of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two soap dispenser's in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn right and face the sink to your left.
Take the green cream bottle from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the toilet on your right.
Place the green cream bottle in the can near the toilet in front of you.
Turn right and face the can near the toilet on your left.
Take the green bottle out of the can in front of you.
Turn around then right and face the toilet on your right.
Place the green bottle in the can near the toilet in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a bottle in the can near the toilet.

high_descs: walk to face sinks
pick up blue pumper bottle from counter between sinks
walk to face toilet
put pumper bottle into bin to right of toilet
walk to face toilet tank top
pick up blue pumper bottle from toilet tank top
turn to face bin
put pumper bottle into bin to right of toilet
anns.task_desc: put two pumper bottles into a bin
